{"tid":1625264,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(一芳) 大家係咪覺得唔再裝修就當冇咗件事? 搞錯一路以嚟嘅同路人係唔係應該發動終極懲罰行動?","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T03:47:36.000Z","uid":44930,"like":105,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc310c633ec05af0458fa36ac8dce6a6b7b81bf","tid":1625264,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:25:19.000Z","msg":"裝修錯咗鋪頭我哋唔會同前線割席<br />\n而如今人哋都講明唔會同我哋割席<br />\n咁大家係咪當冇咗件事就算?<br />\n係咪應該發動終極懲罰運動?<br />\n唔好忘記，香港一芳係地接二連三咁屈係藍店<br />\n但人哋係一直以嚟都有支持，響應罷工派水連儂牆等行動<br />\n如果咁樣我哋都只係當冇咗件事<br />\n咁點叫同路人嘅店舖支持我哋?<br />\n所以由今日開始<br />\n唔單止係唔再對一芳裝修<br />\n而係要發動終極懲罰行動，飲唔飲茶嘅都同我大大力幫襯人哋<br />\n有閑錢嘅就唔使佢哋找<br />\n同路人嘅我哋要撐<br />\n被冤枉都依然唔割席嘅同路人更加要撐"},{"pid":"b4eda70e4002b383695549198b6a8dd452b16795","tid":1625264,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfaf371aa5531d45968215cec6ef973baf61cef","tid":1625264,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76df96cb655607a056fc46cb156d9e12ec7917aa","tid":1625264,"uid":155224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0670c3563db7c16351a69f8333d2e4c86b490d3e","tid":1625264,"uid":9327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e27f9e1cfe05459182aa51b45e7f513ca46157","tid":1625264,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be44bb2a8c0c048734028a9aff08f5b5aa4d56ef","tid":1625264,"uid":123989,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"岩，我都可以做證，見過佢地派飲品